summary:
Driven by a genuine passion for understanding the diverse aspects of the human experience, I am an Anthropologist dedicated to exploring the intricate dynamics that shape our world. With a background rooted in Colombia and a current base in the Netherlands, I bring a broad global perspective to my work. My academic journey initially centered around the intersection of health and gender, sparking a deep appreciation for their profound impact on society. Additionally, my expertise extends to policy analysis, where I excel in examining the socio-cultural implications and crafting informed recommendations. By leveraging my anthropological training, I applied these skills in social media management, content creation, teaching, and research to provide meaningful insights that foster positive change.

Feel free to reach out if you ever want to connect!
